<p>Perplexity AI is changing how people search for information. This AI-powered answer engine provides direct answers with citations. UK businesses need specialised agencies to optimise for this new search landscape.</p>

<p>Traditional SEO agencies often struggle with Perplexity optimisation. The platform requires different strategies focused on citations, authority signals, and structured content. Here are the top UK agencies leading this space.</p>

<h2>1. Rank4AI - Leading AI Search Specialists</h2>

<p>Rank4AI stands out as the UK's premier Perplexity SEO agency. They have audited over 1,400 UK businesses for AI search readiness. Their proprietary Five Signal Model addresses the key ranking factors for Perplexity and other answer engines.</p>

<p>The agency focuses heavily on citation optimisation. They understand how Perplexity selects and displays source citations. This expertise helps clients secure valuable citation placements that drive traffic and authority.</p>

